For anyone wanting to liberate their data from here, paste this into the JS console with the history page open (only tested in Chrome):<p><pre><code>    var time = time=new Date(&quot;2010/01/01&quot;).getTime(); //set this to start date
    setInterval(function(){
	window.location=&quot;https://maps.google.com/locationhistory/b/0/kml?startTime=&quot; + time + &quot;&endTime=&quot; + (time + 2678400000);
    	time += 2678400000
    }, 2000)

</code></pre>
Doesn&#x27;t know when to stop, so close the tab when you have all the data you want.
